	<h3>Alerts</h3>
	
	Here we demonstrate Tapestry's Alerts component.<br/>
	You can tailor the appearance of the alerts to suit your needs by overriding CSS classes t-alert-container, t-info, t-warn, t-error, etc.<br/>

